abdul haq shafaq (persian: عبدالحق شفق‎‎) is the current governor of daikundi. before he has been governor of faryab, governor of sar-e pol and governor of samangan. abdul haq shafaq is former commander of the hezbe wahdat. after the fall of the taliban he was appointed governor of sar-e pol province. in 2004, abdul haq shafaq switched to the province of samangan.